## Commands

```bash
npm ci
make dev
make seed
make test
make test-integration
make eval
make clean
```

## Deliverables

- Passing public tests.
- `results/payment_recovery_report.json` from `make eval`.
- A concise debrief explaining your state model, idempotency decisions, and recovery behavior.

Private tests add harder gateway timeout, idempotency conflict, settlement, duplicate worker, and report-evidence cases.
